    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver or a great project for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has some noticeable scuffs, minor dings, and thinning clear coat in a few spots, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, it starts and runs, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It is a reliable car for its age, offered at a price that reflects its current state.",
