      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of life left? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road, showing some honest wear that reflects its journey. It runs well and offers a comfortable ride, making it a fantastic value for anyone seeking a practical and functional car at a great price!",
