    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional motorcar, currently maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast, exhibiting flawless mechanical integrity and an interior devoid of wear. Every aspect of this specimen has been preserved to the highest standards, reflecting an impeccable provenance and a commitment to rigorous maintenance. We invite serious inquiries to inspect what is undoubtedly one of the finest examples of its kind available on the market today.",
      "price": 46500.0,
